short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Stop doubting yourself. Hide difficulty level of Leetcode problems and conquer them with new vigor

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: How many times have you choked or given up on a Leetcode problem early only because it was tagged as "Hard"? This extension allows you to hide the difficulty level of problems so that you can attack every problem with the same vigor.
